 AI 短剧生成平台\" [ref=e381] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-huobao-drama---ai-短剧生成平台\"\n                    - img [ref=e382]\n                - generic [ref=e384]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e385]:\n                    - strong [ref=e386]: 基于 TypeScript 全栈的 AI 短剧自动化生产平台\n                  - paragraph [ref=e387]:\n                    - link \"Node Version\" [ref=e388] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://nodejs.org\n                      - img \"Node Version\" [ref=e389]\n                    - link \"Vue Version\" [ref=e390] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://vuejs.org\n                      - img \"Vue Version\" [ref=e391]\n                    - link \"License\" [ref=e392] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\n                      - img \"License\" [ref=e393]\n                  - paragraph [ref=e394]:\n                    - link \"功能特性\" [ref=e395] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: \"#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7\"\n                    - text: •\n                    - link \"快速开始\" [ref=e396] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: \"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B\"\n                    - text: •\n                    - link \"部署指南\" [ref=e397] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: \"#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\"\n                - separator [ref=e398]\n                - generic [ref=e399]:\n                  - heading \"📖 项目简介\" [level=2] [ref=e400]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📖 项目简介\" [ref=e401] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-项目简介\"\n                    - img [ref=e402]\n                - paragraph [ref=e404]: Huobao Drama 是一个基于 AI 的短剧自动化生产平台，实现从剧本生成、角色设计、分镜制作到视频合成的全流程自动化。\n                - paragraph [ref=e405]:\n                  - text: 火宝短剧商业版地址：\n                  - link \"火宝短剧商业版\" [ref=e406] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://drama.chatfire.site/shortvideo\n                  - text: 火宝小说生成：\n                  - link \"火宝小说生成\" [ref=e407] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://marketing.chatfire.site/huobao-novel/\n                - generic [ref=e408]:\n                  - heading \"🎯 核心价值\" [level=3] [ref=e409]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎯 核心价值\" [ref=e410] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-核心价值\"\n                    - img [ref=e411]\n                - list [ref=e413]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e414]:\n                    - strong [ref=e415]: 🤖 AI 驱动\n                    - text: ：使用大语言模型解析剧本，提取角色、场景和分镜信息\n                  - listitem [ref=e416]:\n                    - strong [ref=e417]: 🎨 智能创作\n                    - text: ：AI 绘图生成角色形象和场景背景\n                  - listitem [ref=e418]:\n                    - strong [ref=e419]: 📹 视频生成\n                    - text: ：基于文生视频和图生视频模型自动生成分镜视频\n                  - listitem [ref=e420]:\n                    - strong [ref=e421]: 🔄 工作流\n                    - text: ：完整的短剧制作工作流，从创意到成片一站式完成\n                - generic [ref=e422]:\n                  - heading \"🛠️ 技术架构\" [level=3] [ref=e423]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🛠️ 技术架构\" [ref=e424] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#️-技术架构\"\n                    - img [ref=e425]\n                - code [ref=e429]: frontend/ — Nuxt 3 + Vue 3 + TypeScript (纯 CSS，无 UI 框架) backend/ — Hono + Drizzle ORM + Mastra AI Agents + better-sqlite3 configs/ — config.yaml 配置文件 data/ — SQLite 数据库 + 生成资源文件 skills/ — Agent 技能定义 (SKILL.md)\n                - generic [ref=e430]:\n                  - heading \"🎥 作品展示 / Demo Videos\" [level=3] [ref=e431]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎥 作品展示 / Demo Videos\" [ref=e432] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-作品展示--demo-videos\"\n                    - img [ref=e433]\n                - paragraph [ref=e435]: 体验 AI 短剧生成效果：\n                - generic [ref=e436]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e437]:\n                    - strong [ref=e438]: 示例作品 1\n                  - paragraph\n                  - paragraph [ref=e439]:\n                    - strong [ref=e440]: 示例作品 2\n                  - paragraph\n                  - paragraph [ref=e441]:\n                    - link \"点击观看视频 1\" [ref=e442] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://ffile.chatfire.site/cf/public/20260114094337396.mp4\n                    - text: \"|\"\n                    - link \"点击观看视频 2\" [ref=e443] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://ffile.chatfire.site/cf/public/fcede75e8aeafe22031dbf78f86285b8.mp4\n                - separator [ref=e444]\n                - generic [ref=e445]:\n                  - heading \"✨ 功能特性\" [level=2] [ref=e446]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: ✨ 功能特性\" [ref=e447] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-功能特性\"\n                    - img [ref=e448]\n                - generic [ref=e450]:\n                  - heading \"🎭 角色管理\" [level=3] [ref=e451]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎭 角色管理\" [ref=e452] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-角色管理\"\n                    - img [ref=e453]\n                - list [ref=e455]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e456]: ✅ AI 生成角色形象\n                  - listitem [ref=e457]: ✅ 批量角色生成\n                  - listitem [ref=e458]: ✅ 角色图片上传和管理\n                  - listitem [ref=e459]: ✅ 角色音色分配与试听\n                - generic [ref=e460]:\n                  - heading \"🎬 分镜制作\" [level=3] [ref=e461]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎬 分镜制作\" [ref=e462] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-分镜制作\"\n                    - img [ref=e463]\n                - list [ref=e465]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e466]: ✅ AI 自动拆解分镜脚本\n                  - listitem [ref=e467]: ✅ 场景描述和镜头设计\n                  - listitem [ref=e468]: ✅ 分镜图片生成（文生图）\n                  - listitem [ref=e469]: ✅ 宫格图生成、切分与分配\n                  - listitem [ref=e470]: ✅ 帧类型选择（首帧/尾帧/分镜板）\n                - generic [ref=e471]:\n                  - heading \"🎥 视频生成\" [level=3] [ref=e472]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎥 视频生成\" [ref=e473] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-视频生成\"\n                    - img [ref=e474]\n                - list [ref=e476]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e477]: ✅ 图生视频自动生成\n                  - listitem [ref=e478]: ✅ TTS 配音生成\n                  - listitem [ref=e479]: ✅ FFmpeg 单镜头合成（视频 + 音频 + 字幕）\n                  - listitem [ref=e480]: ✅ 整集拼接导出\n                - generic [ref=e481]:\n                  - heading \"📦 资源管理\" [level=3] [ref=e482]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📦 资源管理\" [ref=e483] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-资源管理\"\n                    - img [ref=e484]\n                - list [ref=e486]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e487]: ✅ 素材库统一管理\n                  - listitem [ref=e488]: ✅ 本地存储支持\n                  - listitem [ref=e489]: ✅ 任务进度追踪\n                - generic [ref=e490]:\n                  - heading \"🤖 AI Agents\" [level=3] [ref=e491]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🤖 AI Agents\" [ref=e492] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-ai-agents\"\n                    - img [ref=e493]\n                - paragraph [ref=e495]: 内置 5 个 Mastra Agent，支持数据库配置和 Skill 扩展：\n                - table [ref=e497]:\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e498]:\n                    - row \"Agent 职责\" [ref=e499]:\n                      - columnheader \"Agent\" [ref=e500]\n                      - columnheader \"职责\" [ref=e501]\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e502]:\n                    - row \"script_rewriter 小说 → 格式化剧本改写\" [ref=e503]:\n                      - cell \"script_rewriter\" [ref=e504]:\n                        - code [ref=e505]: script_rewriter\n                      - cell \"小说 → 格式化剧本改写\" [ref=e506]\n                    - row \"extractor 角色 + 场景智能提取与去重\" [ref=e507]:\n                      - cell \"extractor\" [ref=e508]:\n                        - code [ref=e509]: extractor\n                      - cell \"角色 + 场景智能提取与去重\" [ref=e510]\n                    - row \"storyboard_breaker 剧本 → 分镜序列拆解\" [ref=e511]:\n                      - cell \"storyboard_breaker\" [ref=e512]:\n                        - code [ref=e513]: storyboard_breaker\n                      - cell \"剧本 → 分镜序列拆解\" [ref=e514]\n                    - row \"voice_assigner 角色音色自动分配\" [ref=e515]:\n                      - cell \"voice_assigner\" [ref=e516]:\n                        - code [ref=e517]: voice_assigner\n                      - cell \"角色音色自动分配\" [ref=e518]\n                    - row \"grid_prompt_generator 角色/场景/宫格图提示词生成\" [ref=e519]:\n                      - cell \"grid_prompt_generator\" [ref=e520]:\n                        - code [ref=e521]: grid_prompt_generator\n                      - cell \"角色/场景/宫格图提示词生成\" [ref=e522]\n                - generic [ref=e523]:\n                  - heading \"🔌 多厂商适配\" [level=3] [ref=e524]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🔌 多厂商适配\" [ref=e525] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-多厂商适配\"\n                    - img [ref=e526]\n                - table [ref=e529]:\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e530]:\n                    - row \"类型 支持厂商\" [ref=e531]:\n                      - columnheader \"类型\" [ref=e532]\n                      - columnheader \"支持厂商\" [ref=e533]\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e534]:\n                    - row \"图片 OpenAI、Gemini、MiniMax、火山引擎、阿里、Chatfire\" [ref=e535]:\n                      - cell \"图片\" [ref=e536]:\n                        - strong [ref=e537]: 图片\n                      - cell \"OpenAI、Gemini、MiniMax、火山引擎、阿里、Chatfire\" [ref=e538]\n                    - row \"视频 MiniMax、火山引擎/Seedance、Vidu、阿里\" [ref=e539]:\n                      - cell \"视频\" [ref=e540]:\n                        - strong [ref=e541]: 视频\n                      - cell \"MiniMax、火山引擎/Seedance、Vidu、阿里\" [ref=e542]\n                    - row \"TTS MiniMax\" [ref=e543]:\n                      - cell \"TTS\" [ref=e544]:\n                        - strong [ref=e545]: TTS\n                      - cell \"MiniMax\" [ref=e546]\n                - separator [ref=e547]\n                - generic [ref=e548]:\n                  - heading \"🚀 快速开始\" [level=2] [ref=e549]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🚀 快速开始\" [ref=e550] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-快速开始\"\n                    - img [ref=e551]\n                - generic [ref=e553]:\n                  - heading \"📋 环境要求\" [level=3] [ref=e554]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📋 环境要求\" [ref=e555] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-环境要求\"\n                    - img [ref=e556]\n                - table [ref=e559]:\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e560]:\n                    - row \"软件 版本要求 说明\" [ref=e561]:\n                      - columnheader \"软件\" [ref=e562]\n                      - columnheader \"版本要求\" [ref=e563]\n                      - columnheader \"说明\" [ref=e564]\n                  - rowgroup [ref=e565]:\n                    - row \"Node.js 20+ 前后端运行环境\" [ref=e566]:\n                      - cell \"Node.js\" [ref=e567]:\n                        - strong [ref=e568]: Node.js\n                      - cell \"20+\" [ref=e569]\n                      - cell \"前后端运行环境\" [ref=e570]\n                    - row \"npm 9+ 包管理工具\" [ref=e571]:\n                      - cell \"npm\" [ref=e572]:\n                        - strong [ref=e573]: npm\n                      - cell \"9+\" [ref=e574]\n                      - cell \"包管理工具\" [ref=e575]\n                    - row \"FFmpeg 4.0+ 视频处理（必需）\" [ref=e576]:\n                      - cell \"FFmpeg\" [ref=e577]:\n                        - strong [ref=e578]: FFmpeg\n                      - cell \"4.0+\" [ref=e579]\n                      - cell \"视频处理（必需）\" [ref=e580]:\n                        - text: 视频处理（\n                        - strong [ref=e581]: 必需\n                        - text: ）\n                - generic [ref=e582]:\n                  - heading \"安装 FFmpeg\" [level=4] [ref=e583]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 安装 FFmpeg\" [ref=e584] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#安装-ffmpeg\"\n                    - img [ref=e585]\n                - paragraph [ref=e587]:\n                  - strong [ref=e588]: \"macOS:\"\n                - generic [ref=e590]: brew install ffmpeg\n                - paragraph [ref=e591]:\n                  - strong [ref=e592]: \"Ubuntu/Debian:\"\n                - generic [ref=e594]: sudo apt update && sudo apt install ffmpeg\n                - paragraph [ref=e595]:\n                  - strong [ref=e596]: \"Windows:\"\n                  - text: 从\n                  - link \"FFmpeg 官网\" [ref=e597] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://ffmpeg.org/download.html\n                  - text: 下载并配置环境变量\n                - paragraph [ref=e598]: 验证安装：\n                - generic [ref=e600]: ffmpeg -version\n                - generic [ref=e601]:\n                  - heading \"⚙️ 配置文件\" [level=3] [ref=e602]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: ⚙️ 配置文件\" [ref=e603] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#️-配置文件\"\n                    - img [ref=e604]\n                - paragraph [ref=e606]: 复制并编辑配置文件：\n                - generic [ref=e608]: cp configs/config.example.yaml configs/config.yaml\n                - paragraph [ref=e609]:\n                  - text: 配置文件格式（\n                  - code [ref=e610]: configs/config.yaml\n                  - text: ）：\n                - generic [ref=e612]:\n                  - text: \"app: name:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e613]: \"\\\"Huobao Drama API\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"version:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e614]: \"\\\"1.0.0\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"debug: true server: port: 5679 host:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e615]: \"\\\"0.0.0.0\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"cors_origins: -\"\n                  - generic [ref=e616]: \"\\\"http://localhost:3013\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"database: type:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e617]: \"\\\"sqlite\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"path:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e618]: \"\\\"./data/huobao_drama.db\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"storage: type:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e619]: \"\\\"local\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"local_path:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e620]: \"\\\"./data/storage\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"base_url:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e621]: \"\\\"http://localhost:5679/static\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"ai: default_text_provider:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e622]: \"\\\"openai\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"default_image_provider:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e623]: \"\\\"openai\\\"\"\n                  - text: \"default_video_provider:\"\n                  - generic [ref=e624]: \"\\\"doubao\\\"\"\n                - blockquote [ref=e625]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e626]:\n                    - strong [ref=e627]: 说明\n                    - text: ：AI 服务的具体 API Key 和模型参数在 Web 界面的「设置」页面中配置。\n                - generic [ref=e628]:\n                  - heading \"📥 安装依赖\" [level=3] [ref=e629]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📥 安装依赖\" [ref=e630] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-安装依赖\"\n                    - img [ref=e631]\n                - generic [ref=e634]:\n                  - generic [ref=e635]: \"# 克隆项目\"\n                  - text: git clone https://github.com/chatfire-AI/huobao-drama.git cd huobao-drama\n                  - generic [ref=e636]: \"# 安装后端依赖\"\n                  - text: cd backend && npm install\n                  - generic [ref=e637]: \"# 安装前端依赖\"\n                  - text: cd ../frontend && npm install\n                - generic [ref=e638]:\n                  - heading \"🎯 启动项目\" [level=3] [ref=e639]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎯 启动项目\" [ref=e640] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-启动项目\"\n                    - img [ref=e641]\n                - generic [ref=e643]:\n                  - heading \"方式一：开发模式（推荐）\" [level=4] [ref=e644]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 方式一：开发模式（推荐）\" [ref=e645] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#方式一开发模式推荐\"\n                    - img [ref=e646]\n                - paragraph [ref=e648]: 前后端分离，支持热重载：\n                - generic [ref=e650]:\n                  - generic [ref=e651]: \"# 终端1：启动后端\"\n                  - text: cd backend npm run dev\n                  - generic [ref=e652]: \"# 终端2：启动前端\"\n                  - text: cd frontend npm run dev\n                - list [ref=e653]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e654]:\n                    - text: \"前端地址:\"\n                    - code [ref=e655]: http://localhost:3013\n                  - listitem [ref=e656]:\n                    - text: \"后端 API:\"\n                    - code [ref=e657]: http://localhost:5679/api/v1\n                  - listitem [ref=e658]:\n                    - text: 前端自动代理\n                    - code [ref=e659]: /api\n                    - text: 和\n                    - code [ref=e660]: /static\n                    - text: 到后端\n                - generic [ref=e661]:\n                  - heading \"方式二：单服务模式\" [level=4] [ref=e662]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 方式二：单服务模式\" [ref=e663] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#方式二单服务模式\"\n                    - img [ref=e664]\n                - paragraph [ref=e666]: 后端同时提供 API 和前端静态文件：\n                - generic [ref=e668]:\n                  - generic [ref=e669]: \"# 1. 构建前端\"\n                  - text: cd frontend && npm run generate\n                  - generic [ref=e670]: \"# 2. 启动后端\"\n                  - text: cd ../backend && npm start\n                - paragraph [ref=e671]:\n                  - text: \"访问:\"\n                  - code [ref=e672]: http://localhost:5679\n                - generic [ref=e673]:\n                  - heading \"🗄️ 数据库\" [level=3] [ref=e674]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🗄️ 数据库\" [ref=e675] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#️-数据库\"\n                    - img [ref=e676]\n                - paragraph [ref=e678]:\n                  - text: 数据库表在首次启动时自动创建，无需手动迁移。默认路径\n                  - code [ref=e679]: data/huobao_drama.db\n                  - text: ，可通过环境变量覆盖：\n                - generic [ref=e681]: DB_PATH=/path/to/your.db npm start\n                - separator [ref=e682]\n                - generic [ref=e683]:\n                  - heading \"📦 部署指南\" [level=2] [ref=e684]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📦 部署指南\" [ref=e685] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-部署指南\"\n                    - img [ref=e686]\n                - generic [ref=e688]:\n                  - heading \"☁️ 云端一键部署（推荐 3080Ti）\" [level=3] [ref=e689]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: ☁️ 云端一键部署（推荐 3080Ti）\" [ref=e690] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#️-云端一键部署推荐-3080ti\"\n                    - img [ref=e691]\n                - paragraph [ref=e693]:\n                  - text: 👉\n                  - link \"优云智算，一键部署\" [ref=e694] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://www.compshare.cn/images/CaWEHpAA8t1H?referral_code=8hUJOaWz3YzG64FI2OlCiB&ytag=GPU_YY_YX_GitHub_huobaoai\n                - blockquote [ref=e695]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e696]:\n                    - generic [ref=e697]: ⚠️\n                    - strong [ref=e698]: 注意\n                    - text: ：云端部署方案数据请及时存储到本地\n                - separator [ref=e699]\n                - generic [ref=e700]:\n                  - heading \"🐳 Docker 部署（推荐）\" [level=3] [ref=e701]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🐳 Docker 部署（推荐）\" [ref=e702] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-docker-部署推荐\"\n                    - img [ref=e703]\n                - generic [ref=e705]:\n                  - heading \"方式一：Docker Compose（推荐）\" [level=4] [ref=e706]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 方式一：Docker Compose（推荐）\" [ref=e707] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#方式一docker-compose推荐\"\n                    - img [ref=e708]\n                - generic [ref=e711]:\n                  - generic [ref=e712]: \"# 启动服务\"\n                  - text: docker compose up -d\n                  - generic [ref=e713]: \"# 查看日志\"\n                  - text: docker compose logs -f\n                  - generic [ref=e714]: \"# 停止服务\"\n                  - text: docker compose down\n                - generic [ref=e715]:\n                  - heading \"方式二：Docker 命令\" [level=4] [ref=e716]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 方式二：Docker 命令\" [ref=e717] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#方式二docker-命令\"\n                    - img [ref=e718]\n                - generic [ref=e721]:\n                  - generic [ref=e722]: \"# 从 Docker Hub 运行\"\n                  - text: docker run -d \\ --name huobao-drama \\ -p 5679:5679 \\ -v\n                  - generic [ref=e723]: $(pwd)\n                  - text: /data:/app/data \\ -v\n                  - generic [ref=e724]: $(pwd)\n                  - text: /configs/config.yaml:/app/configs/config.yaml \\ --restart unless-stopped \\ huobao/huobao-drama:latest\n                  - generic [ref=e725]: \"# 查看日志\"\n                  - text: docker logs -f huobao-drama\n                - blockquote [ref=e726]:\n                  - paragraph [ref=e727]:\n                    - strong [ref=e728]: 注意\n                    - text: ：Linux 用户需添加\n                    - code [ref=e729]: \"--add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway\"\n                    - text: 以访问宿主机服务\n                - paragraph [ref=e730]:\n                  - strong [ref=e731]: 本地构建\n                  - text: （可选）：\n                - generic [ref=e733]:\n                  - text: docker build -t huobao-drama:latest . docker run -d --name huobao-drama -p 5679:5679 \\ -v\n                  - generic [ref=e734]: $(pwd)\n                  - text: /data:/app/data \\ -v\n                  - generic [ref=e735]: $(pwd)\n                  - text: /configs/config.yaml:/app/configs/config.yaml \\ huobao-drama:latest\n                - paragraph [ref=e736]:\n                  - strong [ref=e737]: Docker 部署优势：\n                - list [ref=e738]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e739]: ✅ 开箱即用，内置 FFmpeg 和默认配置\n                  - listitem [ref=e740]: ✅ 前后端合并为单镜像、单端口\n                  - listitem [ref=e741]: ✅ 环境一致性，避免依赖问题\n                  - listitem [ref=e742]:\n                    - text: ✅\n                    - code [ref=e743]: data/\n                    - text: 目录 volume 挂载，数据持久化\n                - generic [ref=e744]:\n                  - heading \"🔗 访问宿主机服务（Ollama / 本地模型）\" [level=4] [ref=e745]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🔗 访问宿主机服务（Ollama / 本地模型）\" [ref=e746] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-访问宿主机服务ollama--本地模型\"\n                    - img [ref=e747]\n                - paragraph [ref=e749]:\n                  - text: 容器内可通过\n                  - code [ref=e750]: http://host.docker.internal:端口号\n                  - text: 访问宿主机服务。\n                - paragraph [ref=e751]:\n                  - strong [ref=e752]: 配置步骤：\n                - list [ref=e753]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e754]:\n                    - paragraph [ref=e755]: 宿主机启动服务（监听所有接口）：\n                    - generic [ref=e757]: export OLLAMA_HOST=0.0.0.0:11434 && ollama serve\n                  - listitem [ref=e758]:\n                    - paragraph [ref=e759]: 在 Web 界面「设置 → AI 服务配置」中填写：\n                    - list [ref=e760]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e761]:\n                        - text: \"Base URL:\"\n                        - code [ref=e762]: http://host.docker.internal:11434/v1\n                      - listitem [ref=e763]:\n                        - text: \"Provider:\"\n                        - code [ref=e764]: openai\n                      - listitem [ref=e765]:\n                        - text: \"Model:\"\n                        - code [ref=e766]: qwen2.5:latest\n                - separator [ref=e767]\n                - generic [ref=e768]:\n                  - heading \"🏭 传统部署方式\" [level=3] [ref=e769]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🏭 传统部署方式\" [ref=e770] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-传统部署方式\"\n                    - img [ref=e771]\n                - generic [ref=e774]:\n                  - generic [ref=e775]: \"# 1. 构建前端\"\n                  - text: cd frontend && npm run generate && cd ..\n                  - generic [ref=e776]: \"# 2. 启动后端\"\n                  - text: cd backend && npm start\n                - paragraph [ref=e777]: 需要上传到服务器的文件：\n                - code [ref=e780]: \"backend/ # 后端源码 + node_modules frontend/dist/ # 前端构建产物 configs/config.yaml data/ # 数据目录（首次运行自动创建） skills/ # Agent 技能文件\"\n                - generic [ref=e781]:\n                  - heading \"Nginx 反向代理\" [level=4] [ref=e782]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: Nginx 反向代理\" [ref=e783] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#nginx-反向代理\"\n                    - img [ref=e784]\n                - generic [ref=e787]: \"server { listen 80; server_name your-domain.com; location / { proxy_pass http://localhost:5679; proxy_set_header Host $host; proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr; proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for; } }\"\n                - separator [ref=e788]\n                - generic [ref=e789]:\n                  - heading \"🎨 技术栈\" [level=2] [ref=e790]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🎨 技术栈\" [ref=e791] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-技术栈\"\n                    - img [ref=e792]\n                - generic [ref=e794]:\n                  - heading \"后端\" [level=3] [ref=e795]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 后端\" [ref=e796] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#后端\"\n                    - img [ref=e797]\n                - list [ref=e799]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e800]:\n                    - strong [ref=e801]: 运行时\n                    - text: \": Node.js 20+\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e802]:\n                    - strong [ref=e803]: Web 框架\n                    - text: \": Hono\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e804]:\n                    - strong [ref=e805]: ORM\n                    - text: \": Drizzle ORM + better-sqlite3\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e806]:\n                    - strong [ref=e807]: AI Agent\n                    - text: \": Mastra + AI SDK (OpenAI compatible)\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e808]:\n                    - strong [ref=e809]: 视频处理\n                    - text: \": FFmpeg (fluent-ffmpeg)\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e810]:\n                    - strong [ref=e811]: 图片处理\n                    - text: \": Sharp\"\n                - generic [ref=e812]:\n                  - heading \"前端\" [level=3] [ref=e813]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 前端\" [ref=e814] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#前端\"\n                    - img [ref=e815]\n                - list [ref=e817]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e818]:\n                    - strong [ref=e819]: 框架\n                    - text: \": Nuxt 3 (SPA 模式)\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e820]:\n                    - strong [ref=e821]: 语言\n                    - text: \": Vue 3 + TypeScript\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e822]:\n                    - strong [ref=e823]: 路由\n                    - text: \": 文件路由 (Vue Router 4)\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e824]:\n                    - strong [ref=e825]: 样式\n                    - text: \": 纯 CSS + CSS Variables (暗色主题)\"\n                  - listitem [ref=e826]:\n                    - strong [ref=e827]: 图标\n                    - text: \": Lucide Vue\"\n                - separator [ref=e828]\n                - generic [ref=e829]:\n                  - heading \"📝 常见问题\" [level=2] [ref=e830]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📝 常见问题\" [ref=e831] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-常见问题\"\n                    - img [ref=e832]\n                - generic [ref=e834]:\n                  - 'heading \"Q: Docker 容器如何访问宿主机的 Ollama？\" [level=3] [ref=e835]'\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: Q: Docker 容器如何访问宿主机的 Ollama？\" [ref=e836] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#q-docker-容器如何访问宿主机的-ollama\"\n                    - img [ref=e837]\n                - paragraph [ref=e839]:\n                  - text: \"A: 使用\"\n                  - code [ref=e840]: http://host.docker.internal:11434/v1\n                  - text: 作为 Base URL。注意：\n                - list [ref=e841]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e842]:\n                    - text: 宿主机 Ollama 需监听\n                    - code [ref=e843]: 0.0.0.0\n                    - text: ：\n                    - code [ref=e844]: export OLLAMA_HOST=0.0.0.0:11434 && ollama serve\n                  - listitem [ref=e845]:\n                    - text: Linux 用户使用\n                    - code [ref=e846]: docker run\n                    - text: 需添加：\n                    - code [ref=e847]: \"--add-host=host.docker.internal:host-gateway\"\n                - generic [ref=e848]:\n                  - 'heading \"Q: FFmpeg 未安装或找不到？\" [level=3] [ref=e849]'\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: Q: FFmpeg 未安装或找不到？\" [ref=e850] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#q-ffmpeg-未安装或找不到\"\n                    - img [ref=e851]\n                - paragraph [ref=e853]:\n                  - text: \"A: 确保 FFmpeg 已安装并在 PATH 环境变量中。运行\"\n                  - code [ref=e854]: ffmpeg -version\n                  - text: 验证。Docker 部署已内置 FFmpeg。\n                - generic [ref=e855]:\n                  - 'heading \"Q: 前端无法连接后端 API？\" [level=3] [ref=e856]'\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: Q: 前端无法连接后端 API？\" [ref=e857] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#q-前端无法连接后端-api\"\n                    - img [ref=e858]\n                - paragraph [ref=e860]:\n                  - text: \"A: 检查后端是否启动，端口是否正确。开发模式下前端代理配置在\"\n                  - code [ref=e861]: frontend/nuxt.config.ts\n                  - text: 。\n                - generic [ref=e862]:\n                  - 'heading \"Q: 数据库表未创建？\" [level=3] [ref=e863]'\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: Q: 数据库表未创建？\" [ref=e864] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#q-数据库表未创建\"\n                    - img [ref=e865]\n                - paragraph [ref=e867]: \"A: 后端会在首次启动时自动创建所有表，检查日志确认初始化是否成功。\"\n                - separator [ref=e868]\n                - generic [ref=e869]:\n                  - heading \"📋 更新日志\" [level=2] [ref=e870]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 📋 更新日志\" [ref=e871] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-更新日志\"\n                    - img [ref=e872]\n                - generic [ref=e874]:\n                  - heading \"v2.0.0 (2026-04)\" [level=3] [ref=e875]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: v2.0.0 (2026-04)\" [ref=e876] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#v200-2026-04\"\n                    - img [ref=e877]\n                - generic [ref=e879]:\n                  - heading \"🚀 重大更新\" [level=4] [ref=e880]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🚀 重大更新\" [ref=e881] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-重大更新\"\n                    - img [ref=e882]\n                - list [ref=e884]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e885]:\n                    - text: 项目全面迁移至 TypeScript 技术栈\n                    - list [ref=e886]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e887]: 后端：Hono + Drizzle ORM + better-sqlite3\n                      - listitem [ref=e888]: 前端：Nuxt 3 + Vue 3\n                      - listitem [ref=e889]: AI Agent：Mastra 框架\n                  - listitem [ref=e890]:\n                    - text: 重做单集工作台 UI 和生产流程\n                    - list [ref=e891]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e892]: 更紧凑的控制台布局\n                      - listitem [ref=e893]: 重做分镜编辑区\n                      - listitem [ref=e894]: 重做配音、镜头图、视频、合成、导出界面\n                  - listitem [ref=e895]: 新增 Docker 部署支持，前后端合并为单镜像\n                  - listitem [ref=e896]: 增加运行时 Skill 加载机制\n                  - listitem [ref=e897]:\n                    - text: 扩展多厂商媒体 Adapter\n                    - list [ref=e898]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e899]: 图片：OpenAI、Gemini、MiniMax、火山引擎、阿里\n                      - listitem [ref=e900]: 视频：MiniMax、火山引擎/Seedance、Vidu、阿里\n                      - listitem [ref=e901]: TTS：MiniMax\n                  - listitem [ref=e902]: 增加宫格图生成、切分和重新分配流程\n                  - listitem [ref=e903]: 优化本地文件处理与参考图按需转码\n                - generic [ref=e904]:\n                  - heading \"v1.0.4 (2026-01-27)\" [level=3] [ref=e905]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: v1.0.4 (2026-01-27)\" [ref=e906] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#v104-2026-01-27\"\n                    - img [ref=e907]\n                - list [ref=e909]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e910]: 引入本地存储策略，规避外部资源链接失效\n                  - listitem [ref=e911]: Base64 参考图嵌入式传输\n                  - listitem [ref=e912]: 修复镜头切换状态重置问题\n                  - listitem [ref=e913]: 添加场景迁移至章节\n                - generic [ref=e914]:\n                  - heading \"v1.0.3 (2026-01-16)\" [level=3] [ref=e915]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: v1.0.3 (2026-01-16)\" [ref=e916] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#v103-2026-01-16\"\n                    - img [ref=e917]\n                - list [ref=e919]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e920]: SQLite 纯 Go 驱动，支持 CGO_ENABLED=0 跨平台编译\n                  - listitem [ref=e921]: 优化并发性能（WAL 模式）\n                  - listitem [ref=e922]: Docker 跨平台支持 host.docker.internal\n                - generic [ref=e923]:\n                  - heading \"v1.0.2 (2026-01-14)\" [level=3] [ref=e924]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: v1.0.2 (2026-01-14)\" [ref=e925] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#v102-2026-01-14\"\n                    - img [ref=e926]\n                - list [ref=e928]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e929]: 修复视频生成 API 响应解析问题\n                  - listitem [ref=e930]: 添加 OpenAI Sora 视频端点配置\n                  - listitem [ref=e931]: 优化错误处理和日志输出\n                - separator [ref=e932]\n                - generic [ref=e933]:\n                  - heading \"🤝 贡献指南\" [level=2] [ref=e934]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: 🤝 贡献指南\" [ref=e935] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#-贡献指南\"\n                    - img [ref=e936]\n                - paragraph [ref=e938]: 欢迎提交 Issue 和 Pull Request！\n                - list [ref=e939]:\n                  - listitem [ref=e940]: Fork 本项目\n                  - listitem [ref=e941]:\n                    - text: 创建特性分支 (\n                    - code [ref=e942]: git checkout -b feature/AmazingFeature\n                    - text: )\n                  - listitem [ref=e943]:\n                    - text: 提交改动 (\n                    - code [ref=e944]: git commit -m 'Add some AmazingFeature'\n                    - text: )\n                  - listitem [ref=e945]:\n                    - text: 推送到分支 (\n                    - code [ref=e946]: git push origin feature/AmazingFeature\n                    - text: )\n                  - listitem [ref=e947]: 开启 Pull Request\n                - paragraph [ref=e948]: 常用检查命令：\n                - generic [ref=e950]: cd backend && npm run typecheck cd ../frontend && npm run build\n                - separator [ref=e951]\n                - generic [ref=e952]:\n                  - heading \"API 配置站点\" [level=2] [ref=e953]\n                  - 'link \"Permalink: API 配置站点\" [ref=e954] [cursor=pointer]':\n                    - /url: \"#api-配置站点\"\n                    - img [ref=e955]\n                - paragraph [ref=e957]:\n                  - text: 2 分钟完成配置：\n                  - link \"API 聚合站点\" [ref=e958] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://api.ch