{"type":"message","id":"4714e14e","parentId":"7652730e","timestamp":"2026-04-05T13:31:44.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Got the full tweet content. Now let me analyze the self-media related projects (27-35) and answer the user's question about whether there are costs beyond AI model fees (i.e., developer/platform fees).\n\nLet me look at the relevant projects:\n\n27. MoneyPrinterTurbo - AI short video generation\n28. NarratoAI - AI movie review + auto editing\n29. VideoLingo - Video translation/dubbing tool\n30. social-auto-upload - Multi-platform auto upload\n31. md2wechat-skill - WeChat article automation\n32. XiaohongshuSkills - Xiaohongshu automation\n33. baoyu-skills - Content creation skills\n34. huobao-drama - AI short drama generation (we already analyzed this)\n35. Toonflow - Novel to short drama\n\nThe user's question is specifically: are there costs BEYOND AI model fees? i.e., do you need to pay the developers of these tools?\n\nLet me check the licenses and payment models of these projects. Most are open source on GitHub. Let me think about what I know:\n\n- MoneyPrinterTurbo - open source, free\n- NarratoAI - open source, free\n- VideoLingo - open source, free\n- social-auto-upload - open source, free\n- huobao-drama - CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (non-commercial)\n- Toonflow - need to check\n\nThe main costs would be:\n1. AI API costs (OpenAI, etc.) - user already knows about these\n2. Platform costs - some might have paid tiers\n\nLet me give a comprehensive answer about the self-media automation tools from this list.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"内容拿到了！这条推文整理了 40 个赚钱相关的 GitHub 仓库，其中 **自媒体自动化** 部分是 #27-35。我来帮你分析一下费用问题：\n\n---\n\n## 📱 自媒体自动化项目（#27-35）费用分析\n\n先说结论：**这些工具本身几乎全部免费开源，不用给开发者付费。** 主要成本是 AI API 调用费。\n\n### 🆓 完全免费（开源）\n\n| # | 项目 | 做什么 | 许可证 |\n|---|------|--------|--------|\n| 27 | **MoneyPrinterTurbo** | AI 短视频生成（文案+配音+字幕+素材） | 开源免费，但维护较差 |\n| 28 | **NarratoAI** | AI 影视解说+自动剪辑 | 开源免费 |\n| 29 | **VideoLingo** | 视频翻译+配音（搬运用） | 开源免费 |\n| 30 | **social-auto-upload** | 抖音/小红书/B站自动发布 | 开源免费 |\n| 31 | **md2wechat-skill** | 公众号自动排版发布 | 开源免费 |\n| 33 | **baoyu-skills** | 多平台配图生成+发布 | 开源免费 |\n\n### ⚠️ 有使用限制\n\n| # | 项目 | 限制 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 34 | **huobao-drama** | CC BY-NC-SA 4.0，**不能商用** |\n| 32 | **XiaohongshuSkills** | 开源但小红书有反爬风险，多账号操作可能封号 |\n| 35 | **Toonflow** | 需要确认许可证 |\n\n---\n\n## 💰 你真正要花的钱（AI API 费用）\n\n这才是大头，跟工具开发者无关，是给 AI 服务商的：\n\n| 用途 | 便宜方案 | 贵方案 | 大致单条视频成本 |\n|------|----------|--------|------------------|\n| **文案生成** | DeepSeek (~¥0.01/条) | GPT-4 (~¥0.5/条) | ¥0.01-0.5 |\n| **TTS 配音** | Edge TTS（免费） | MiniMax (~¥0.3/条) | ¥0-0.3 |\n| **文生图** | 火山引擎/硅基流动 (~¥0.05/张) | Midjourney (~¥0.5/张) | ¥0.5-5（多条分镜） |\n| **文生视频** | Seedance/可灵 (~¥0.5-2/条) | Runway (~¥5-10/条) | ¥2-50（多条分镜） |\n| **字幕翻译** | 免费方案多 | - | ¥0-0.1 |\n\n**总结：做一条 AI 短视频，成本从几毛钱到几十块不等，取决于你用多贵的模型。** 用国产平替（DeepSeek + 可灵 + 火山引擎）可以把单条成本压到 **¥3-10** 以内。\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 对我们最有价值的几个\n\n按实用性排序：\n\n1. **MoneyPrinterTurbo** — 最成熟，但维护差，建议 fork 自己改\n2. **NarratoAI** — 影视解说赛道很火，全自动化\n3. **social-auto-upload** — 多平台分发刚需\n4. **baoyu-skills** — 宝玉出品，跟我们的 OpenClaw skill 体系兼容\n\n要我挑几个最有用的克隆下来本地研究一下吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":6803,"output":1482,"cacheRead":65459,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775395876549}}
