{"type":"message","id":"c37f534a","parentId":"c3ce7e0b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:23:20.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about which AI models are best suited for writing \"abstract\" (比较抽象的) novels in Chinese on the Chinese internet. \"抽象\" in Chinese internet culture can mean weird, absurdist, surreal, or unconventional content. This is a creative/content creation question.\n\nLet me think about what I know about different AI models' capabilities for creative writing in Chinese, especially for absurdist/surreal fiction.\n\nLet me search for some current information on this topic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个问题挺有意思，\"抽象小说\"在中文互联网语境下通常指荒诞、意识流、无厘头、赛博朋克等风格的创作。我帮你分析一下各模型的写作能力："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_53d5d3fa66724f4fb08691ca","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-mrbeast/skills/news-aggregator-skill/SKILL.md","limit":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":108018,"output":275,"cacheRead":228,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775715763411,"responseId":"20260409142245dd0599f71f324a65"}}
