{"type":"message","id":"87cc16b3","parentId":"a0b7d0da","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:25:02.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking the same question again. I just answered this in my previous response. Maybe they didn't see it or want a different take. Let me just refer them to my previous answer since I already gave a comprehensive response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"刚回答过这个问题！你往上翻一下就能看到完整分析。\n\n简单回顾一下核心结论：\n\n| 场景 | 最佳模型 |\n|------|----------|\n| **意识流/荒诞派** | Claude Sonnet 4（天花板） |\n| **赛博朋克/科幻** | GPT-4o |\n| **网文无厘头/搞笑** | 通义千问 |\n| **长篇连载** | Kimi（200K 上下文） |\n| **性价比之王** | DeepSeek R1（几乎免费） |\n\n**终极搭配：DeepSeek R1 写初稿 → Claude Sonnet 润色加抽象感**\n\n要我用不同模型各写一段对比看看吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":1965,"output":246,"cacheRead":108244,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110455,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775715891399,"responseId":"202604091424534eeb79ac45e54c3e"}}
